"},{"pid":"d83a5218945da5762d00ce1e5f38b62176ba2c47","tid":2394563,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"香港狗官死全家"},{"pid":"375f6d8c835210b1ff05e6ad9031a452a2bc8016","tid":2394563,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda55399dbac94b09e85c4e3afd9349124652dba","tid":2394563,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76a15b64726b3aea70b5d750b1c288322cdbf781","tid":2394563,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"前年8月有示威者在尖沙嘴聚集，其間防暴警撲倒一名前空姐，指她用雷射筆照射警員眼睛。她受審後襲警罪成，判囚3個月，早前提出上訴，高等法院今開庭聆訊。上訴一方提出新證據，指影片顯示當時有一名與上訴人衣著相似、身處附近位置的女子在人群當中，並沒做出任何施襲動作，而該女子正是上訴人。她亦就刑期提出上訴，惟法官李運騰指上訴人行為具挑釁性，謂：「大家差唔多散band......呢個時候撩是鬥非，係咪乞人憎吖？係咪想令警察發嬲打人，俾人影相？唔係咁㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n上訴一方今由大律師黃錦娟代表，指出影片顯示一名與上訴人身穿相似裝束、身處相似位置的女子，在上訴人遭警員制服前身處人群當中；但她沒有如警員證人所言，做出舉手照射雷射光的襲擊動作。<br />\n<br />\n大律師認為，該名女子便是上訴人。審訊時警員證人供稱上訴人兩度用雷射筆施襲，惟當時片段僅顯示第二次照射的情況；警員卻表示兩次襲擊都是來自同一人、從同一個位置照射雷射光。大律師指，若果片段顯示第二次施襲者不是上訴人，便可推斷第一次施襲者也不是她。在當時混亂的現場環境中，不排除警員認錯人及拉錯人。<br />\n<br />\n李官表示，單靠影片無法確定片中女子與上訴人的位置接近，但辯方沒舉證責任，不必證明該女子必定是上訴人，只需證明兩者相似，重點在於會否因而對警員證供構成疑問。<br />\n<br />\n至於刑期上訴，上訴方指本案控罪沒有量刑標準。上訴人僅被指用雷射筆照射了警員一秒，律政司呈交的案例情節卻較本案嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n惟李官指重點不是雷射光造成的傷害，否則會控告傷人或襲擊等罪，強調判刑須考慮案件本質，而上訴人行為具挑釁性，謂：「大家差唔多散band喇，仲有人照射警察，除咗撩是鬥非，都冇乜其他可能。你呢個時候撩是鬥非，係咪乞人憎吖？係咪想令警察發嬲打人，俾人影相？唔係咁㗎嘛！」上訴方同意，但強調本案罪行性質相對輕微。<br />\n<br />\n李官又提醒，刑期上訴有危機。上訴方稱明白刑期「可升可減」，並強調重點在於定罪上訴。案件押後至下月24日再聆訊，被告繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/R75R44UYWZHJTGTY2LYHKLPNTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FR75R44UYWZHJTGTY2LYHKLPNTM%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=17ee7f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FR75R44UYWZHJTGTY2LYHKLPNTM%2F&h=b3aef4f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/R75R44UYWZHJTGTY2LYHKLPNTM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"發嬲就可以打人？"},{"pid":"90eb60c982e039c231a0b34bb55daa04cfbc32ec","tid":2394563,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"會員全職港豬死左未<br />\n未既上黎講2句啦<br />\n大律師公會繼續奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300f20b9e1386ad6a7b0a915ef682309e9db92b3","tid":2394563,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db9a9cc613b0a7cca969f4f99e956efdbd185d07","tid":2394563,"uid":334720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5aba4bb1e5a799bff1713deabbd5375b3180d225","tid":2394563,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"李運騰轉死性？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"你重睇一次好d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢咁講即係覺得班狗打人係正常<br />\n並鬧事主有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"即係暗示班狗亂打人"},{"pid":"9632981a26194e1b37d2888a797d34f76c28ba3b","tid":2394563,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4693a9ce5a0ada158e36eb8cb865551110deade1","tid":2394563,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"我一直唔明<br />\n點解辯方上訴就刑期「可升可減」<br />\nDOJ班賤種上訴就最多「可升或維持不變」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"其實一般情況係<br />\nDOJ基本上係唔會review sentence<br />\n被告Appeal Sentence果時亦都好少加刑，即使係無ground鳩申請都只係刑期唔計等候上訴嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n不過依加個情況就無人知<br />\n但鳩估今次都唔會加刑"},{"pid":"242c3f98f5305cdafd4c387ad2acab6cc8eda7d5","tid":2394563,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"警察發嬲就可以打人係咩邏輯"},{"pid":"38906e663f759895776ee2858694c7519b80a342","tid":2394563,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"屌勁慘，嗰日睇片見個女仔畀班狗捉住揸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb00361a409b398e9654f9b610c170edc7c9a4bb","tid":2394563,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1efe8f9b66295df442246c6edcf846cb78e7488d","tid":2394563,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab747b1b7a629387405bd11eac4317d58a51520","tid":2394563,"uid":21545,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"李運騰係咪收咗order 做白面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"大波驊出黎放曬風<br />\n而家咪扮下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>《金融時報》日前引消息指，不少企業因擔心中國政策會影響香港法治環境，正考慮將香港從法律合同中的仲裁地區名單中剔除，即代表合同不會使用本港法律及仲裁法院處理。<span class=\"red\">律政司司長鄭若驊發表網誌回應，指香港一直是提供國際法律和爭議解決服務的主要所在地，仲裁方面具領導地位。她認為，香港的優勢及在「一國兩制」下，加上大灣區發展等機遇，將有助進一步鞏固香港作為促成交易，以及爭議解決服務的國際法律樞紐，地位無可取替。</span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"仲裁同 一國兩制有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪想話香港法律比中國優勝"},{"pid":"c3e4838ef358dc2049bd464ae48d4b7e39bc17f2","tid":2394563,"uid":300740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aab747b1b7a629387405bd11eac4317d58a51520","tid":2394563,"uid":21545,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"李運騰係咪收咗order 做白面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"你中文幾時差咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecf9364b64b30a44b0d3428c22f62f8e6eec19b","tid":2394563,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"大律師公會又扮盲<br />\n只要次次司法迫害都扮盲<br />\n依然可以膠吹香港無司法迫害<br />\n公會有夏博義呢條偽君子果然識玩左"},{"pid":"811503a1c01fbd5e4d7ad1478e7c17e81910c046","tid":2394563,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca91ce3662dc402513b6e7c0b7f1aac0313f7f","tid":2394563,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢個官幾老實喎，popo發嬲會打人嘅！<br />\n想問下咁樣係合法㗎？"},{"pid":"fdd4217234f8001fdaff53e977d4d4c8a106745a","tid":2394563,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb00361a409b398e9654f9b610c170edc7c9a4bb","tid":2394563,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1efe8f9b66295df442246c6edcf846cb78e7488d","tid":2394563,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab747b1b7a629387405bd11eac4317d58a51520","tid":2394563,"uid":21545,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"李運騰係咪收咗order 做白面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"大波驊出黎放曬風<br />\n而家咪扮下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>《金融時報》日前引消息指，不少企業因擔心中國政策會影響香港法治環境，正考慮將香港從法律合同中的仲裁地區名單中剔除，即代表合同不會使用本港法律及仲裁法院處理。<span class=\"red\">律政司司長鄭若驊發表網誌回應，指香港一直是提供國際法律和爭議解決服務的主要所在地，仲裁方面具領導地位。她認為，香港的優勢及在「一國兩制」下，加上大灣區發展等機遇，將有助進一步鞏固香港作為促成交易，以及爭議解決服務的國際法律樞紐，地位無可取替。</span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"仲裁同 一國兩制有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪想話香港法律比中國優勝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"去得某個地方做仲裁<br />\n就係信當地既 司法制度有獨立性 / 唔受任何干預<br />\n而家做到出面doj 9告 + 紅官鄭紀航一定判罪成<br />\n咁邊個仲敢黎香港仲裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公民黨omdb 個幾個舊年開始扮傻仔係咁Spin 「法治死左未」<br />\n甚至去埋美國叫唔好制裁<br />\n就係知一被美國定性係三權合作迫害既話<br />\n香港仲裁成行一定收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFYI 大波驊未入doj 之前就係做仲裁出身<br />\n佢比任何人都清楚金融時報話唔再搵香港仲裁有咩影響<br />\n當時搵佢傾一粒鐘要6000港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>香港國際仲裁中心和新加坡國際仲裁中心都被公認為位列世界上最好的仲裁中心之列。倫敦瑪麗女王大學（Queen Mary University of London）的一項調查發現，<span class=\"red\">香港國際仲裁中心是&ldquo;歐洲以外最受歡迎的首選仲裁機構&rdquo;、全球第三大仲裁機構，以及進步最快的仲裁地。</span>新加坡國際仲裁中心緊隨其後，排名第四，進步程度僅次於前者，位居第二。<br />\n規則<br />\n香港國際仲裁中心最先於1985年成立，通常使用2013年的《管理仲裁規則》進行國際與國內仲裁。新加坡國際仲裁中心於1991年開始運營，主要使用自己的規則，目前使用的是2013年版仲裁規則。兩家機構也將根據當事人的要求使用其他機構的規則，並能管理臨時仲裁。<br />\n費用<br />\n兩者的費用分三部分：登記或備案費，行政費和仲裁員費。二者總體費用通常相似，新加坡國際仲裁中心略高。<br />\n例如，<span class=\"red\">一起 100萬美元的爭議，香港國際仲裁中心的費用約為62,000美元，</span>新加坡國際仲裁中心的費用約為65,000美元。<span class=\"red\">一起5億美元的爭議，香港國際仲裁中心的費用為445,000美元</span>，新加坡國際仲裁中心的費用約為555,000美元。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e4d7bc40aeb9d3991ce103d77ba61e81a204746a","tid":2394563,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c831b5def159963831843d66475538bbd76a6a3b","tid":2394563,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63680ab1bfe066a4310818e344a209ffc809e9cb","tid":2394563,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83c76bb2d35be90cec86121c7a351502bc1fcd4d","tid":2394563,"uid":25468,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"aab747b1b7a629387405bd11eac4317d58a51520","tid":2394563,"uid":21545,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"李運騰係咪收咗order 做白面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" cl